{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.920", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.240", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.040", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.520", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In diesem Jahr j\u00e4hrt sich zum zehnten Mal der Beginn der Bankenkrise im Jahr\u00a02008 mit der Pleite der Lehman-Bank. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.040", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zehn Jahre, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.160", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die f\u00fcr Finanzpolitiker wei\u00df Gott kein Zuckerschlecken waren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.360", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Von der Bankenkrise\u00a02008 sind wir dann nahtlos in die Finanzkrise gerutscht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.120", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und 2010 hat unser ehemaliger Finanzminister Wolfgang Sch\u00e4uble einen Haushaltsentwurf mit einem Defizit von 86\u00a0Milliarden Euro in der Planung \u00fcbernommen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "44.000", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "2014 haben wir es zum ersten Mal geschafft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "44.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "46.240", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "einen ausgeglichenen Haushalt vorzulegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "46.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.560", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und 2019 werden wir das erste Mal die Maastricht-Kriterien, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.520", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auch hinsichtlich des Schuldenstandes im Vergleich zum BIP, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "55.160", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wieder einhalten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "55.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "57.040", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Da die Opposition in den n\u00e4chsten Tagen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "57.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.600", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sie ist ja schon kr\u00e4ftig dabei\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "59.800", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wieder alles miesredet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "59.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "62.640", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was in diesem Haushalt und in den letzten Jahren geschafft worden ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "62.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "63.320", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denke ich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "63.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "63.800", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist es Zeit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "63.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "66.240", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "einmal innezuhalten und Danke zu sagen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "66.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "73.240", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir diese Krisen gut \u00fcberstanden haben und dass Deutschland nach zehn Jahren heute wieder gut dasteht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "73.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "75.800", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Danke zu sagen den Menschen in diesem Land, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "75.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "78.120", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die das mit ihrer Arbeit erreicht haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "78.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "80.640", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die in der Krisensituation Ruhe behalten haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "80.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "84.200", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Danke zu sagen auch den Kolleginnen und Kollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "84.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "85.800", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die mitgeholfen haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "85.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "89.680", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir jetzt wieder in einer so guten Situation sind."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "89.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "93.880", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u2013\u00a0Auch an die Sparerinnen und Sparer. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "93.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "95.480", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ein Teil unserer Arbeit war, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "95.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "96.640", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sicherzustellen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "96.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "98.680", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Wirtschaft in diesem Land wieder auf die F\u00fc\u00dfe kommt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "98.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "100.000", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und daf\u00fcr zu sorgen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "100.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "102.240", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Sparerinnen und Sparer sicher sein k\u00f6nnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "102.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "106.120", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass ihr Verm\u00f6gen auch in Zukunft Dividenden bringt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "106.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "107.760", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben diesen Stand erreicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "107.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "113.360", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "obwohl wir in der letzten Legislaturperiode B\u00fcrgerinnen und B\u00fcrger um 25\u00a0Milliarden Euro entlastet haben: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "113.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "114.440", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "durch einen h\u00f6heren Grundfreibetrag, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "114.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "115.880", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "durch einen h\u00f6heren Kinderfreibetrag, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "115.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.680", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "durch mehr Kindergeld, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "121.760", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "durch einen h\u00f6heren Entlastungsbetrag f\u00fcr Alleinerziehende und durch Entlastung bei der kalten Progression."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "121.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "126.240", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Insbesondere Familien standen in den letzten Jahren im Fokus unserer Politik. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "126.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "126.880", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Kindergeld- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "126.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "133.120", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Freibetragserh\u00f6hungen machen allein im Jahr\u00a02018 eine Entlastung in H\u00f6he von 2,2\u00a0Milliarden Euro aus. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "133.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "136.760", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese Entlastungen setzen wir in dieser Legislaturperiode fort. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "136.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "140.360", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir werden das Kindergeld um weitere 25\u00a0Euro und entsprechend auch den Kinderfreibetrag erh\u00f6hen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "140.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "142.200", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir beginnen 2019 mit einem ersten Schritt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "142.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "148.640", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dadurch werden Familien weitere 1,1\u00a0Milliarden Euro zur Verf\u00fcgung haben."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "148.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "154.240", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Neben Steuern und Abgaben ist das Thema Wohnen f\u00fcr Familien ein Kostenfaktor. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "154.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "157.200", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir brauchen mehr finanzierbaren Wohnraum. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "157.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "161.840", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dabei ist uns ein gesunder Mix aus Eigentum und Miete wichtig."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "161.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "164.480", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Den sozialen Wohnungsbau f\u00f6rdern wir schon seit Jahren: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "164.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.040", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Seit 2017 sind pro Jahr 1,5\u00a0Milliarden Euro vorgesehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "176.200", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und 2020/21 werden wir noch einmal 2\u00a0Milliarden Euro draufsatteln\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "176.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "176.840", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Geld, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "176.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "179.880", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das eigentlich in die Investitionsquote des Bundes, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "179.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "181.880", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die heute mehrfach kritisiert wurde, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "181.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "183.280", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mit eingerechnet werden m\u00fcsste; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "183.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "185.840", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn auch dabei handelt es sich um Investitionen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "185.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "187.480", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und Investitionen sind nicht nur gut, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "187.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "188.400", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn sie vom Staat kommen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "188.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "189.280", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern auch dann, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "189.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "193.400", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn sie von der privaten Wirtschaft oder von Privatpersonen get\u00e4tigt werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "193.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "196.440", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber auch die Eigentumsbildung bei Familien ist uns wichtig. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "196.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "201.720", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00dcber das Baukindergeld wollen wir r\u00fcckwirkend zum 1.\u00a0Januar 2018 Familien helfen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "201.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "203.440", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die g\u00fcnstigen Zinsen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "203.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "205.040", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die es zurzeit f\u00fcr Kredite gibt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "205.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "207.720", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auszunutzen und damit Wohneigentum zu schaffen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "207.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "213.160", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Familien mit zwei Kindern werden 24\u00a0000\u00a0Euro Zuschuss erhalten k\u00f6nnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "213.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "215.760", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und wir werden mit den L\u00e4ndern in Verhandlungen treten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "215.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "219.080", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass diese Entlastung noch umfangreicher wird, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "219.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "225.040", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "indem etwa bei der Grunderwerbsteuer ein Freibetrag f\u00fcr Familien eingef\u00fchrt wird."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "225.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "227.800", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wichtig sind aber ebenso bezahlbare Mietwohnungen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "227.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "229.200", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb bin ich froh, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "229.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "230.040", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass angek\u00fcndigt wurde, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "230.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "230.920", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "daf\u00fcr zu sorgen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "230.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "235.440", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass noch in diesem Jahr eine steuerliche Sonderabschreibung f\u00fcr Mietwohnungsneubau eingef\u00fchrt wird. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "235.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "236.960", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist ein zweiter Anlauf, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "236.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "239.680", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nachdem wir bereits in der letzten Legislaturperiode einen Anlauf unternommen hatten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "239.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "240.880", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben uns jetzt verst\u00e4ndigt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "240.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "241.640", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "f\u00fcr Bauantr\u00e4ge, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "241.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "244.280", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die ab 1.\u00a0September 2018 gestellt werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "244.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "246.720", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "steuerliche Sonderabschreibungen zu gew\u00e4hren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "246.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "248.520", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dabei ist nicht mehr die Rede davon, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "248.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "251.680", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "diese von einer Mietpreisbremse und einer Kappungsgrenze abh\u00e4ngig zu machen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "251.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "252.680", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und auch nicht mehr ist die Rede davon, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "252.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "256.040", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass diese Sonderabschreibung nur in bestimmten Ballungsgebieten gilt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "256.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "258.160", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch das sind Investitionen; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "258.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "266.760", 
   "id": "s000088", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sie umfassen allein 2019\u00a0 240\u00a0Millionen Euro und steigen bis 2021 auf 900\u00a0Millionen Euro. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "266.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "269.600", 
   "id": "s000089", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese Gelder geh\u00f6ren zum Punkt Investitionen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "269.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "274.600", 
   "id": "s000090", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
